title: War of the Roses: She Found Something on His Computer
description: This week is a little different because Carly is not trying to see if her partner is cheating BUT if her best friend's husband is cheating.  The reason for this is because her friend's husband gave her his old computer and she found some things in the recycling bin that is making her question his loyalty.
